## 2. Exhaustive API Endpoint Roadmap

### IAM (Authentication)
- `POST /auth/login`, `POST /auth/register`, `GET /auth/me`
- `PATCH /users/profile`, `POST /auth/logout`

### Academic (Courses & Grades)
- `GET /courses`, `GET /courses/:id`, `POST /courses` (Staff)
- `GET /enrollments`, `POST /enrollments` (Enroll Student)
- `PATCH /grades/bulk` (Lecturer), `GET /grades/history/:studentId`
- `GET /attendance/report`, `POST /attendance/check-in`

### Training (Quests & Tasks)
- `GET /quests`, `GET /quests/:id`, `POST /quests/accept`
- `PATCH /quests/task/complete` (Updates progress and checks for quest completion)
- `GET /player/stats` (XP, Coins, Level, Badges)

### Career (Jobs & Internships)
- `GET /jobs`, `POST /jobs`, `POST /applications`
- `GET /internship/logs`, `POST /internship/logs`
- `PATCH /internship/documents/:id/status` (Staff Approval)
- `GET /talent/search` (Company Filtering with Skill Gap)

### Operations (Finance & Personnel)
- `GET /budget`, `POST /budget` (Staff)
- `GET /personnel`, `GET /cooperation`, `POST /cooperation`
- `GET /workload`, `POST /workload` (Lecturer/Staff)
- `GET /subscription/plans`, `POST /subscription/payment` (Company)

### Student Support (Requests & Appointments)
- `GET /requests`, `POST /requests`, `POST /requests/:id/comment`
- `GET /appointments`, `POST /appointments`, `PATCH /appointments/:id/status`
- `GET /office-hours/:lecturerId`

### System (Audit & Notifications)
- `GET /notifications`, `PATCH /notifications/:id/read`
- `GET /audit-logs` (Admin Only), `GET /reports/system-usage`

